{"tid":1094186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【父子天上再聚】陳百強父親陳鵬飛離世 終年96歲","createTime":"2019-04-06T06:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T08:25:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"612044b24dd82cb46deb8c8d3522164605022e6e","tid":1094186,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"中環金寶錶行創辦人、已故巨星陳百強父親陳鵬飛，證實於昨日早上（5日）與世長辭，享壽96歲。<br />\n陳鵬飛近年行動不便需以輪椅代步，但仍不時到鍾愛的陸羽茶室飲茶，至於其一手創立的錶行已交由陳百強大哥陳百靈打理，對於陳鵬飛逝世之事，《蘋果》曾致電陳百靈查詢，但對方未有接電話。<br />\n而資深傳媒人查小欣今早於社交網站證實陳老先生去世的消息，查小欣貼出一張與陳鵬飛及陳百靈的合照，並寫道：「陳百強爸爸昨天走了，據知老人家有福氣，走得安祥，吃完早餐，上了洗手間後頭暈，跟着便走了，享高壽96歲。陳爸爸如今與Danny父子相見了。」<br />\n《蘋果》致電查小欣詢問，她回覆：「我收到佢哋（陳爸爸親友）嗰邊通知，confirm咗，以前我因為識Danny所以識得陳爸爸，有時都會落佢中環錶行探吓佢，舊年9月Danny紀念活動，我都見到陳爸爸，佢精神好好，成餐飯食晒，完全冇問題，所以知道呢個消息好突然，不過老人家走得好舒服，冇痛苦，大家放心。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190406/large/1554529964_ade9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190406%2Flarge%2F1554529964_ade9.jpg&h=f76beb01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190406/large/1554529964_45da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190406%2Flarge%2F1554529964_45da.jpg&h=39ec8b21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190406/large/1554529964_a0f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190406%2Flarge%2F1554529964_a0f3.jpg&h=efd9ed3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190406/59456427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190406%2F59456427&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYq2paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=74db2c73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190406%2F59456427&h=4cbb153b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190406/59456427</a>"},{"pid":"104ecaca234234f7d9d30ccaf3a742d6568d6b36","tid":1094186,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T06:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />RIP"},{"pid":"0ca719c31e522e1110a4becf4fbd3557cc745433","tid":1094186,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff05fe0d2f4d4a4524b5ef071e1e625273d04a5","tid":1094186,"uid":139863,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"無病無痛咁樣走真係有褔氣"},{"pid":"2c89093832d5e0c08ec3e63bf1009499de4a0367","tid":1094186,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:16:04.000Z","msg":"教到個仔好有氣質<br />\n<br />\n陳生 RIP"},{"pid":"2f726dfcd3abff3be49648dedd6d515e176b539f","tid":1094186,"uid":163056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"查小欣爆足一週<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0c79b96bb84be909908d5d672bdad4352ab12a","tid":1094186,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:22:54.000Z","msg":"願Danny兩父子同在天堂安好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810b6b0b8f5ad895447959c94ceb7077fc4102d5","tid":1094186,"uid":164239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:24:35.000Z","msg":"\\I/ Rip"},{"pid":"81ff048c12f46899e4d76cfec6d4a0608a8d2acf","tid":1094186,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"走得舒服就好了"},{"pid":"3d74a8ee5728f0e7840621d532ebe6c8d9c3deb9","tid":1094186,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dis